trans-unit.source: Exposes an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.IValidator"></xref> references.
trans-unit.target: Viser en matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.IValidator"> </xref> referanser.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: Each ValidatorCollection reference is associated with a validation server control contained on the requested page.
trans-unit.target: Hver ValidatorCollection referanse er knyttet til en validering serverkontroll finnes på den forespurte siden.

trans-unit.source: These controls add themselves to this collection when the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Init> event of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> object is handled.
trans-unit.target: Disse kontrollene legge til seg selv i denne samlingen når den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Init>hendelsen til den <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>objektet håndteres.</xref:System.Web.UI.Page> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Init>

trans-unit.source: They remove themselves when the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Unload> event of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> object is handled.
trans-unit.target: De fjernet når den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Unload>hendelsen til den <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>objektet håndteres.</xref:System.Web.UI.Page> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Unload>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class inherits both of these methods from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>Klassen arver begge disse metodene fra <xref:System.Web.UI.Control>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control> </xref:System.Web.UI.Page>

trans-unit.source: You can access this collection, its methods, and its properties through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.Validators%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til denne samlingen, metodene og egenskapene til det <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.Validators%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Page.Validators%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If the tested condition of any validator in this collection fails, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.IsValid%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis testet tilstanden for alle validerer i denne samlingen mislykkes, den <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.IsValid%2A?displayProperty=fullName>er satt til `false`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Page.IsValid%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ValidatorCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ValidatorCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified validation server control to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ValidatorCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Legger til den angitte validering serverkontrollen til den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ValidatorCollection"> </xref> samling.

trans-unit.source: When added to the <xref:System.Web.UI.ValidatorCollection> collection of a <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> object through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.Validators%2A> property, the <xref:System.Web.UI.IValidator> implementation takes part in validation.
trans-unit.target: Når du legger til den <xref:System.Web.UI.ValidatorCollection>samling av en <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>objekt via den <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.Validators%2A>egenskapen den <xref:System.Web.UI.IValidator>implementering tar del i validering.</xref:System.Web.UI.IValidator> </xref:System.Web.UI.Page.Validators%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Page> </xref:System.Web.UI.ValidatorCollection>

trans-unit.source: Its <xref:System.Web.UI.IValidator.Validate%2A> method is called together with the <xref:System.Web.UI.IValidator.Validate%2A> methods of all other validators.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.IValidator.Validate%2A>metoden sammen med den <xref:System.Web.UI.IValidator.Validate%2A>metoder for alle andre validerer.</xref:System.Web.UI.IValidator.Validate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.IValidator.Validate%2A>

trans-unit.source: All validators then share in determining whether the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> object as a whole is valid.
trans-unit.target: Alle validerer da kan dele til å bestemme om den <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>objekt som en helhet er gyldig.</xref:System.Web.UI.Page>
